Aurvista Gold Corp.


            
            Aurvista Gold Corp. is a gold exploration and development company, which engages in the acquisition, exploration, and development of mineral resources properties. Its project includes the Douay Gold project. The company was founded on June 3, 2010 and is headquartered in Montréal, Canada.

            
